Name: Pop Culture Crossover
Description: Amir’s Winner Category - Pick a song whose title includes the title of a movie, TV show, or book (but it cannot be the theme song or have any actual connection to that movie, TV show, or book)

Name: Personal Favorite Strikes Back
Description: Pick a song with under 15 Million plays on Spotify

Name: We need a name! Give us a name!
Description: Pick a song by an Artist that shares a name with or contains the name of anyone in the Music League chat. Can be first name, last name or a nickname.

Name: You think I give a damn about a Grammy?
Description: Pick a song that was Grammy nominated for either Song of the Year or Record of the Year

Name: Name Drop it like it’s Hot
Description: Song mentions another musical artist in the lyrics (who is not involved in the making of the song). Nicknames  are fine (eg, “Pac).”
